- 10 PT visits in last 12 months; no surgery history
- Meds: naproxen 500 mg BID, gabapentin 600 mg TID, cyclobenzaprine PRN

### Chronic Disease
- **Type 2 Diabetes** — A1c 8.1%
- **Hypertension** — BP 142/88
- **Hyperlipidemia** — LDL 118
- Meds: metformin, glipizide, lisinopril, HCTZ, atorvastatin, aspirin 81 mg

### Respiratory
- **Chronic bronchitis** — FEV1: 60% predicted, FEV1/FVC: 62%
- 3 exacerbations in last 12 months; enrolled in pulmonary rehab
- Exposure history: burn pit, dust/smoke
- Meds: umeclidinium/vilanterol daily, albuterol HFA PRN, roflumilast

### Other
